Everybody's going crazy at work.

50
00:02:55,382 --> 00:02:59,214
I don't think they should, Dad.
Card catalogs are much better.

51
00:02:59,344 --> 00:03:00,755
Yeah. I like 'em better too.

52
00:03:00,888 --> 00:03:03,842
I think you've got a
problem with your report.

53
00:03:03,975 --> 00:03:06,726
- What's the problem?
- Isn't there a line missing here?

54
00:03:06,811 --> 00:03:08,139
You're right. Darn.

55
00:03:08,229 --> 00:03:10,387
I'll have to print the entire thing over.

56
00:03:10,523 --> 00:03:13,607
Can't I use the printer first?
My professor will kill me

57
00:03:13,693 --> 00:03:15,900
if I don't have his paper
turned in tomorrow.

58
00:03:16,028 --> 00:03:18,152
Seiji Amasawa.

59
00:03:18,281 --> 00:03:20,239
Here he is again.

60
00:03:21,285 --> 00:03:24,452
Shizuku, time to put the
books away and go to bed.

61
00:03:24,538 --> 00:03:26,162
OK, Dad. Good night.

62
00:03:34,173 --> 00:03:37,340
Yep. I knew I had seen that name before.

63
